title: 'High expectations; low result'
body: The contents and advertising was great. So I felt it would turn out great, just like the market leader. But no. It's an average soap considering its contents. Mildly creamy, cleans average, won't melt away fast, smells almost like the market leader, dries skin a bit and needs post bath moisturising. Overall, yeah, recommended when available for lesser rate.
